{"tid":2056479,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"柒婆聽日行會做返件好事宣佈足球場籃球場重開得唔得？","createTime":"2020-06-08T17:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T12:31:24.000Z","uid":241774,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"98210c3960627f789a708937355f4a034b96290c","tid":2056479,"uid":241774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T17:08:25.000Z","msg":"足籃場3月底封之前一直冇傳出過感染個案，而家連主題公園、書展都開返，捨得解封未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0206294281d3bf235131ac443c2525232fc3725e","tid":2056479,"uid":241774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T17:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d107e60b901645906beded5c02bf57ca3a537581","tid":2056479,"uid":241774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:25:09.000Z","msg":"集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b570bd54ab2a0f4f604b397289c24be0e96cd1","tid":2056479,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09d6470e959c067850a367daae47f6f1e65633a","tid":2056479,"uid":27664,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"777 ： 你估球場係海洋公園呀？"},{"pid":"a8943107292d2cf07fad4bf83c9190f4402a6418","tid":2056479,"uid":241774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:19:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/303559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.c